data.description: You will love coming home to this stately residence with refreshing pool gently nestled on a private, oversized lot only minutes from Lake Ray Hubbard. Upon entrance you are welcomed by the inviting living room with cozy fireplace, followed by a lovely dining area. The chef in your family will enjoy the beautifully updated gourmet kitchen with ample counter & cabinet space, gas range, and white cabinetry. Huge Master Retreat has luxurious bath and is complete with dual sinks, soaking tub and separate shower. Privacy is not a concern as all bedrooms with recently installed luxury vinyl plank flooring are conveniently positioned upstairs. You will be delighted with the energy efficiency of this home as all windows have recently been replaced. Secluded backyard is an entertainer's delight with covered patio, freshly replastered sparkling pool, and no neighbors looking in! Convenient location offers easy access to major thoroughfares, and countless shops, restaurants & attractions nearby.
